query: SELECT dusun from kartu_ibu_registration where userID='user12' group by dusun

SELECT kartu_ibu_registration.dusun as desa, count(*) as linakes_laki_bulan_lalu FROM kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan inner join kartu_anc_visit on kartu_anc_visit.motherid = kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.motherid inner join kartu_ibu_registration on kartu_ibu_registration.kiId = kartu_anc_visit.kiid where kartu_ibu_registration.userid =  'user12' and kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.jeniskelamin='laki' and kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.penolong != 'dukun' and kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.submissionDate between '2015-01-01' and '2015-11-31' group by kartu_ibu_registration.dusun
